{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                              // hydrogen // tour // animation"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Animation System for Product Tours"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This module provides the motion vocabulary for tour transitions:"},{"LineComment":" | - Easing curves (bounded, named presets + custom cubic-bezier)"},{"LineComment":" | - Spring physics configuration"},{"LineComment":" | - Morph transitions (spotlight shape morphing)"},{"LineComment":" | - Animation composition"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Design Philosophy"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | All animations are described as pure data. The runtime interprets these"},{"LineComment":" | descriptions to produce actual motion. This enables:"},{"LineComment":" | - Deterministic animations (same config = same motion)"},{"LineComment":" | - Composable animation primitives"},{"LineComment":" | - Spring physics for natural feel"},{"LineComment":" | - Respect for reduced motion preferences"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Usage"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ```purescript"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Tour.Animation as Anim"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Use presets"},{"LineComment":" | tooltipAnim = Anim.fadeSlideIn Anim.Bottom Anim.springSnappy"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Custom easing"},{"LineComment":" | customEase = Anim.cubicBezier 0.34 1.56 0.64 1.0"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Compose animations"},{"LineComment":" | combined = Anim.sequence [fadeIn, slideIn, scaleUp]"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Module Structure"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This is a leader module that re-exports from submodules:"},{"Lin